mono-tools
------------------------------------------
Collection of tools for the Mono CSharp environment:
* gasnview - ASN.1 viewer
* gnunit   - NUnit framework GUI
* monodoc  - documentation viewer and monodoc tools wrapper

Runtime requirements:
  gconf-sharp2-2.16.0-1
  glade-sharp2-2.10.1-1
  glib-sharp2-2.10.1-1
  gnome-sharp2-2.16.0-1
  gtk-sharp2-2.10.1-1
  gtkhtml-sharp2-2.16.0-1
  mono-1.2.4-1
  monodoc-1.2.4-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  cygwin-1.5.24-2
  autoconf2.5-2.61-1
  automake1.9-1.9.6-2
  cygport-0.3.5-1
  gawk-3.1.5-4
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1
  pkg-config-0.21-1
  sed-4.1.5-2

Canonical website:
  http://www.mono-project.com/

Canonical download:
  http://go-mono.com/sources-latest/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack mono-tools-1.2.4-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./mono-tools-1.2.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mono-tools-1.2.4-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/mono-tools-1.2.4-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

